root: ^I feel like time doesn't even matter anymore.
^We're all just sitting around, just waiting to figure out what's going on. None of us know what to do.
^Yeah, it's hard to process, isn't it?
^Not really. It's dead. I'm more than capable of understanding that, even if it's sad.
^The hardest thing to process is what to do next. All we can do is sit around and wait. But I have to wonder, what are we waiting for?
